    <title>Abstract from stored procedures</title>
    <para>
        As a performance optimization you may, in exceptional cases, use stored procedures. Providing access to
        information via well defined services allows you to introduce or remove such optimizations without having to 
        make any changes to the processes which provide or consume data.
    </para>
